{"tid":2240400,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我妹對我嘅關心用一句話‘你係唔係有目的’嚟作回應？做兄長，你會點做？","createTime":"2020-10-12T15:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T08:35:06.000Z","uid":378580,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"61d8528624269d8f8e9e6b976bb4bc167dc486a2","tid":2240400,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"啱啱沖完涼當然順道問我妹沖咗未，我話佢剛家內跳完舞應該有汗出，原意係基於衞生理由問佢沖咗未，點知佢話唔關我事，仲話我咁問係唔係有目的，你哋聽到這句後，會點？<br />\n<br />\n希望有人評評理。"},{"pid":"36694b13a0f43f48845369ac9167f10a9f06495d","tid":2240400,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"入房打J <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7003be0ae452cc5f85c74364640b744b70b06eb","tid":2240400,"uid":83466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"會扯哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3f07ddeb3bdfe69664d97dbf72bb9ab4a3631c","tid":2240400,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"好minor姐清"},{"pid":"03aa86e6eb9b526057e57a87ae43a221c2c6fe0a","tid":2240400,"uid":55598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"答佢：ok 咁你以後唔好沖"},{"pid":"41166a493d28f2397c7577dfd81bf210f33d4dfe","tid":2240400,"uid":151858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"會覺得尷尬 好似老豆老母吹你去沖涼咁 <br />\n仲要強調我出汗 作為呀妹會覺得尷尬<br />\n同埋真係關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔舒服會自己去沖涼架啦點解要你提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c3de6854ef19630dd225ef6e520d50032f5ad","tid":2240400,"uid":251549,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"首先唔好衝動 冷靜一下<br />\n嘗試理解佢點解會咁講 設身處地諗下<br />\n而唔好執住佢句說落去<br />\n因為好多時人都唔係想講字面意思 有時用字會無意重咗😢<br />\n<br />\n當然下一步係想體諒佢定撩交嗌就睇你想點<br />\n<br />\n咁我就當然建議撩交嗌👍<br />\n佢咁大反應即係有弱點 應該係好介意人地點睇佢<br />\n你可以唔經意咁講唔怪得咁臭啦 或者直接啲話佢好唔衛生之類<br />\n<br />\n總之切記唔好畀佢拖住走 一跟你就中左佢伏<br />\n做個設身處地 理解人地感受嘅人<br />\n仁者無敵 咁你就立於不敗之地😉"},{"pid":"df695911e6fce822a9f75a99905f8a43281b3d45","tid":2240400,"uid":164022,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"咪直接講嫌你臭囉 咩目的呀 臭親你阿哥呀"},{"pid":"e17f4c21329b31170fda74f145c3186d576bdc61","tid":2240400,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03aa86e6eb9b526057e57a87ae43a221c2c6fe0a","tid":2240400,"uid":55598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"答佢：ok 咁你以後唔好沖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"你呢句，我真係頭先駁佢，講咗出嚟，有啲咁嘅細妹頂心頂肺"},{"pid":"cea804ff27a99b04c0a498341c19cfaf2371ceff","tid":2240400,"uid":349439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"1. 你阿妹幾歲？如果十幾歲青春期咁都好正常嘅，始終男女有別會覺得有少少尷尬然後串串貢<br />\n2. 你平時係咪都態度好鬼差、有事要幫先好聲好氣嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果係嘅話咁唔怪得你阿妹覺得你有目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87b265f5f3ae668045c7b398b088f48ad0f588e","tid":2240400,"uid":282700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"佢知你個撚樣想裝佢沖涼打J啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n穿煲勒....."},{"pid":"653fb4d74632cd394b2e100125e77836845bba69","tid":2240400,"uid":378580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cea804ff27a99b04c0a498341c19cfaf2371ceff","tid":2240400,"uid":349439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime